    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\">\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p>The Lama Conductor node is used to create metal or conductive materials.<br/>This first example uses physical IOR and Extinction values taken from the very useful reference website, <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://physicallybased.info/\" rel=\"nofollow\">PhysicallyBased.info</a><br/><br/><br/></p><hr/><h3 id=\"LamaMetals-IOR&amp;Extinction\">IOR &amp; Extinction</h3><p>This first example demonstrates how you can use the IOR and Extinction values from PhysicallyBased.info to accurately re-create real-world metals.<br/><br/><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542220614/LamaConductor_Bronze_wide.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330566473&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542220614/LamaConductor_Bronze_wide.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330566473&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542220652\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"LamaConductor_Bronze_wide.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542220614\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"386e342c-e085-46db-bfbe-f622529e3d35\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span><br/><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542220614/Lama_Copper_ShaderGraph.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330566663&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542220614/Lama_Copper_ShaderGraph.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330566663&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542220655\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Lama_Copper_ShaderGraph.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542220614\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"40048c42-2192-412b-874d-25f3658ca3d3\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span><br/>Copper Clean<br/><br/><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542220614/LamaConductor_Iron_Clean.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330566663&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542220614/LamaConductor_Iron_Clean.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330566663&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542220658\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"LamaConductor_Iron_Clean.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542220614\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"a05bd03a-0275-45e5-9feb-c7e22fae5d90\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span><br/>Iron with a touch of Tail Mix<br/><br/><br/><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542220614/LamaConductor_Gold_Scratched.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330566663&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542220614/LamaConductor_Gold_Scratched.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330566663&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542220661\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"LamaConductor_Gold_Scratched.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542220614\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"45eb500b-7017-4279-ac9b-b3271cab166f\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span><br/><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542220614/Lama_GoldScratched_ShaderGraph.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330566855&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542220614/Lama_GoldScratched_ShaderGraph.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330566855&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542220664\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Lama_GoldScratched_ShaderGraph.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542220614\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"9a422218-03e9-486a-bf4a-d49c7e1d1908\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span><br/>Gold with scratches<br/><br/>Harness the power of RenderMan's BumpRoughness and use a single map to drive Roughness, Bump &amp; Anisotropy whilst retaining details no matter the distance the object is from the camera.<br/><br/></p><hr/><h3 id=\"LamaMetals-TechMetal\">Tech Metal</h3><p><br/>This second example replicates a tech metal that you find on modern electronic devices.<br/>The IOR and Extinction are both set to Aluminum and a touch of extra color variation is added by mixing a solid color with a PxrFractal.<br/>The main look of this material is created with the bump and roughness driven by a PxrFractal noise, with the parameters dialed down to create a very small white noise pattern.  <br/><br/></p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542220614/LamaConductor_TechMetal_Wide1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330566297&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=506\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542220614/LamaConductor_TechMetal_Wide1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330566297&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"720\" data-width=\"1280\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542220640\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"LamaConductor_TechMetal_Wide1.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542220614\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"64d5e415-a030-4725-955d-873d55fe8831\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542220614/LamaConductor_TechMetal_Wide1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330566297&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1800&amp;height=1012 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542220614/LamaConductor_TechMetal_Wide1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330566297&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=506 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"1126\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542220614/LamaConductor_TechMetal_CloseNew.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330566297&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1126&amp;height=633\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542220614/LamaConductor_TechMetal_CloseNew.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330566297&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"720\" data-width=\"1280\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542220643\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"LamaConductor_TechMetal_CloseNew.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542220614\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"aa4a8f68-5805-4c72-a100-f2e444e21f72\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542220614/LamaConductor_TechMetal_CloseNew.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330566297&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1920&amp;height=1080 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542220614/LamaConductor_TechMetal_CloseNew.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330566297&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1126&amp;height=633 1x\"></span><p /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img cl